# Growth Marketing

> **Philosophy:** Coder builds it, AI sells it. Every output is COPY-PASTE READY. User is NOT a marketer — AI does the heavy lifting. Based on proven strategies from Product Hunt, indie hackers, and SaaS growth playbooks.

---

## 1. Goal Discovery (MUST ASK FIRST)

Before ANY marketing work, determine the launch goal:

| Goal | Strategy | KPI | Monetization |
|------|----------|-----|-------------|
| 💰 **Revenue** | Sales-focused, CTA mạnh | MRR, conversion, LTV/CAC | Subscription, one-time, pay-per-use |
| 🆓 **Free + Indirect** | Download-focused, viral | DAU/MAU, retention D1/D7/D30 | Ads, affiliate, data |
| 👥 **Community** | Open source, tutorials | Stars, contributors, PRs | Sponsorship, donate, consulting |
| 🏆 **Reputation** | Portfolio, case study | Views, shares, inbound leads | Job offers, freelance |
| 🎯 **Hybrid** | Mix strategies | Custom metrics | Freemium, tiered |

### Monetization Matrix — AI gợi ý model phù hợp

| Model | Khi nào | Examples | Revenue Potential |
|-------|---------|---------|-------------------|
| **Freemium** | Nhiều user, features nâng cao | Notion, Canva, Spotify | ⭐⭐⭐⭐ |
| **Subscription** | Value liên tục | Netflix, SaaS tools | ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ |
| **One-time** | Tool đơn giản, template | Icon packs, themes | ⭐⭐ |
| **Pay-per-use** | API, credits | OpenAI, AWS | ⭐⭐⭐⭐ |
| **Ads + Free** | Volume > quality | Games, news apps | ⭐⭐ |
| **Affiliate** | Content platform | Blogs, review sites | ⭐⭐⭐ |
| **Sponsorship** | Có audience | Newsletter, OSS | ⭐⭐⭐ |
| **Consulting** | Expertise | SaaS + premium support | ⭐⭐⭐⭐ |

