## 5. Landing Page (Proven High-Converting Structure)

Based on 2025 conversion optimization research.

### Structure (MUST FOLLOW)
```
1. HERO (above the fold)
   ├── Headline: 1 clear benefit (not feature)
   ├── Subheadline: How it works in 1 sentence
   ├── CTA button: Action verb + benefit ("Save 2 hours/day")
   ├── Hero image/video: Product in action
   └── Trust signal: "500+ users" or partner logos

2. PROBLEM SECTION
   ├── 3 pain points (user relates emotionally)
   └── "Sound familiar?" transition

3. SOLUTION SECTION (3 features max)
   ├── Feature 1: [Benefit, not feature name]
   ├── Feature 2: [Benefit, not feature name]
   └── Feature 3: [Benefit, not feature name]

4. SOCIAL PROOF
   ├── 3 testimonials (photo + name + role)
   ├── Metrics: "X users", "Y% improvement"
   └── Trust badges / media mentions

5. PRICING (if paid)
   ├── 2-3 tiers max
   ├── Highlight recommended tier
   ├── Annual discount visible
   └── "Free trial" or "Money-back guarantee"

6. FAQ (top 5 objections)
   └── Address: price, security, migration, support, cancellation

7. FINAL CTA (repeat hero CTA)
   └── Urgency element if appropriate

8. FOOTER
   └── Legal, privacy, social links
```

### Critical Rules
- Load time < 3 seconds
- Mobile-first responsive
- Single CTA (no competing links)
- No navigation menu (landing page ≠ website)
- Social proof above the fold if possible

