## 6. Payment Setup (Localized, Updated 2026)

### Strategy by Goal
```
💰 Revenue + VN indie → SePay (free, auto-verify)
💰 Revenue + VN consumer → MoMo (phổ biến nhất)
💰 Revenue + Global SaaS → Stripe (best API)
💰 Revenue + Global indie → LemonSqueezy (handles tax)
🆓 Free → Donate: Buy Me A Coffee, Ko-fi
👥 Community → GitHub Sponsors, Open Collective
🎯 Hybrid → Freemium: Free tier + paid upgrade
```

### 🇻🇳 Vietnam Payment (Updated 2026)
| Provider | Type | Fee | Integration | Best For |
|----------|------|-----|-------------|----------|
| **SePay** | Bank transfer auto | Free | REST API, webhook | Indie dev, startup. Auto-verify bank transfers |
| **MoMo** | E-wallet | 1-2% | SDK, QR | Consumer app, wide reach |
| **VNPay** | Gateway | 1.5-2% | SDK | Enterprise, multi-bank |
| **ZaloPay** | E-wallet | 1-2% | API | Zalo ecosystem users |
| **Stripe VN** | Card | 2.9% | Best API | SaaS, international cards |

### 🇯🇵 Japan Payment
| Provider | Type | Fee | Best For |
|----------|------|-----|----------|
| **PayPay** | QR | 1.6-1.98% | Most popular, 60M+ users |
| **Stripe JP** | Card | 3.6% | SaaS, recurring |
| **Konbini** | Cash at store | ¥130-300/tx | Users preferring cash |
| **LINE Pay** | E-wallet | 2.45% | LINE ecosystem |
| **Paidy** | BNPL | % | Young users |

### 🇨🇳 China Payment
| Provider | Type | Fee | Best For |
|----------|------|-----|----------|
| **WeChat Pay** | Super app | 0.6% | #1 in-app payment |
| **Alipay** | E-wallet | 0.6% | Cross-border, B2B |
| **UnionPay** | Card | varies | Enterprise |

### 🌍 Global Payment
| Provider | Type | Fee | Best For |
|----------|------|-----|----------|
| **Stripe** | Gateway | 2.9%+30¢ | #1 for devs, best API |
| **Paddle** | MoR | 5%+50¢ | Auto tax for 200+ countries |
| **LemonSqueezy** | MoR | 5%+50¢ | Indie SaaS, simple |
| **Gumroad** | Marketplace | 10% | Digital products, creators |
| **PayPal** | E-wallet | 2.9%+30¢ | US/EU consumers |

