## 7. Launch Calendar (30-Day, Detailed)

### Pre-Launch Sprint (Day -14 to -1)
```
Day -14: Start "build in public" posts
Day -10: Set up analytics (Plausible/GA)
Day -7:  Teaser post — "Something big coming..."
Day -5:  Behind-the-scenes — "Here's what I'm building..."
Day -3:  Sneak peek — screenshot/video demo
Day -2:  Final testing + prepare all content
Day -1:  "Launching TOMORROW!" — build hype
         → Schedule all posts for D-day
         → Email waitlist "Get ready!"
```

### Launch Week (Day 1-7)
```
Day 1 (LAUNCH DAY):
  00:01 — Submit Product Hunt (if global)
  08:00 — Post all channels simultaneously
  08:00-23:00 — Respond to EVERY comment
  12:00 — Share milestone "100 users!"
  20:00 — Thank you post

Day 2: Share first metrics + user reactions
Day 3: Repost best user feedback
Day 4: "Tips & tricks" content
Day 5: First testimonial spotlight
Day 7: Week 1 recap + metrics
```

### Growth Sprint (Day 8-30)
```
Day 8:  Feature request collection
Day 10: First feature update (ship fast!)
Day 14: Tutorial / how-to content
Day 17: User spotlight / case study
Day 21: Community event (AMA, live demo)
Day 25: Second feature update
Day 28: "Month 1" retrospective
Day 30: Celebrate milestone + plan Month 2
```

