## 8. Viral Loop Design

### Framework
```
User gets value → Shares naturally → Friend sees → Friend signs up → LOOP

Types:
1. INHERENT: Product requires sharing (Zoom, WhatsApp)
2. INCENTIVIZED: Rewards for sharing (Dropbox, Uber)
3. SOCIAL: User showcases results (Spotify Wrapped)
4. EMBEDDED: "Powered by [Product]" (Typeform, Calendly)
```

### Double-Sided Rewards (Proven)
```
Both referrer AND friend get something:
- Dropbox: 500MB free storage → 3900% growth in 15 months
- Uber: Free ride for both → global expansion
- PayPal: $10 cash for both → viral early growth

Template for AI:
"Mời bạn bè → Bạn được [X], bạn bè được [Y]"
```

### Gamification
```
Tiers:
🥉 3 referrals → Badge "Early Supporter"
🥈 10 referrals → 1 month Premium free
🥇 25 referrals → Lifetime free + "Ambassador" title

Leaderboard: Top referrers visible (monthly reset)
```

---

## 9. Post-Launch Growth (RETENTION FIRST)

### Product-Market Fit Score
```
Sean Ellis Test: Survey users
"How would you feel if you could no longer use [Product]?"
  A) Very disappointed → TARGET: 40%+
  B) Somewhat disappointed
  C) Not disappointed

Score:
> 40% "very disappointed" = PMF achieved ✅
  20-40% = Getting there, iterate
  < 20% = Pivot or major changes needed ❌
```

### Key Metrics per Stage

| Stage | Primary Metric | Target | Action if Below |
|-------|---------------|--------|-----------------|
| 🌱 0-100 users | Retention D7 | >25% | Fix onboarding |
| 🌿 100-1K users | NPS | >30 | Interview users |
| 🌳 1K-10K users | MRR growth | >10%/mo | Optimize funnel |
| 🔥 10K+ users | NRR | >100% | Upsell/expand |

### Retention Benchmarks (SaaS 2025)
| Metric | Good | Great | Elite |
|--------|------|-------|-------|
| Monthly churn | <5% | <3% | <1% |
| NRR | >100% | >110% | >120% |
| D1 retention | >40% | >60% | >80% |
| D7 retention | >20% | >35% | >50% |
| D30 retention | >10% | >20% | >30% |

### Onboarding (TTFV — Time to First Value)
```
Goal: User experiences core value within FIRST SESSION
- Reduce steps to "aha moment"
- Target: < 2 minutes to value
- Remove all friction (no credit card, no long signup)

Checklist:
☐ Welcome screen (1 sentence: what to do first)
☐ Guided first action (interactive, not text)
☐ First win celebration (confetti, message)
☐ Second action suggestion
```

