## 10. Success Milestones (AI celebrates + guides)

```
🌱 0-10 users:
   "Tập trung làm 10 user THẬT SỰ yêu product"
   Action: Interview mỗi user, fix mọi feedback

🌿 10-100 users:
   "Tìm 1 kênh hiệu quả nhất, double down"
   Action: Test 3 channels, pick winner

🌳 100-1K users:
   "Tối ưu onboarding, giảm churn"
   Action: A/B test, optimize TTFV

🔥 1K-10K users:
   "Scale kênh marketing + thêm revenue stream"
   Action: Hire/automate, add pricing tiers

💎 10K+ users:
   "Bạn có BUSINESS thật sự. Tối ưu unit economics"
   Action: Focus LTV/CAC ratio > 3:1
```
